auh mnu`K hr roz hr vyly prmwqmw dy fr-Adb ivc itikAw rihMdw hY, qy aus fr-Adb dI brkiq nwl Awpxy mn nUM mwr ky (ivkwrW vloN mwr ky ivkwrW vl dI) dOV-B`j dUr krI r`Kdw hY ]5]
ijs mnu`K ny (Awpxy mn dI ivkwrW vl dI) dOV-B`j mukw leI, aus ny sdw Awqmk AwnMd mwixAw[
gurU dI ikrpw nwl aus ny sB qoN au~cI Awqmk AvsQw hwsl kr leI[
jIvn nUM piv`qR krn vwlI gurbwxI dI shwieqw nwl aus dw mn piv`qR ho igAw, auh Awqmk Afolqw ivc itk ky sdw prmwqmw dy gux gWdw rihMdw hY ]6]
(pMifq) vYd SwsqR isimRqIAW (Awidk Drm-pusqk) hornW nUM pVH pVH ky suxWdw rihMdw hY,
pr Awp mwieAw dI Btkxw ivc pY ky kurwhy ipAw rihMdw hY[ auh AslIAq nUM nhIN smJdw[
gurU dI d`sI syvw krn qoN ibnw auh Awqmk AwnMd nhIN mwx skdw, du`K hI du`K (pYdw krn vwlI) kmweI krdw rihMdw hY ]7]
(pr ieh swrI Kyf prmwqmw dy Awpxy h`Q ivc hY[ sB jIvW ivc ivAwpk ho ky prmwqmw) Awp hI (sB kuJ) krdw hY[ iks nUM koeI AwK skdw hY (ik qUM kurwhy jw irhw hYN)?
iksy nUM smJwx dI loV qdoN hI pY skdI hY, jy auh (Awp) kurwhy ipAw hoieAw hovy[
hy nwnk! prmwqmw Awp hI (sB jIvW ivc ivAwpk ho ky sB kuJ) kr irhw hY qy (jIvW pwsoN) krw irhw hY, auh Awp hI (srb-ivAwpk ho ky Awpxy) nwm ivc hI lIn ho skdw hY ]8]7]8]
