pRBU Awp hI (ijn@W mnu`KW nUM) Awqmk Afolqw dy (rMg) ivc rMgdw hY,
sRySt ipAwr (dy rMg) ivc rMgdw hY, ijn@W nUM gurU dy Sbd ivc (joV ky ieh) rMg cwVHdw hY,
auhnW dw mn rMigAw jWdw hY auhnW dw srIr rMigAw jWdw hY, auhnW dI jIB (nwm-) rMg ivc gUVHI lwl ho jWdI hY[ gurU auhnW nUM pRBU dy fr-Adb ivc r`K ky pRBU dy ipAwr ivc joV ky nwm-rMg cwVHdw hY ]1]
mYN sdw auhnW qoN sdky kurbwn jWdw hW jo aus prmwqmw nUM Awpxy mn ivc vsWdy hn ijs nUM iksy dw fr ^qrw nhIN[
ijn@W ny gurU dI ikrpw nwl inrBau prmwqmw dw iDAwn DirAw hY, prmwqmw auhnW nUM gurU dy Sbd ivc joV ky zhr-rUp sMswr-sMmudr qoN pwr lMGw lYNdw hY (Bwv, aus sMswr-smuMdr qoN pwr lMGWdw hY ijs dw moh Awqmk jIvn vwsqy zhr vrgw hY) ]1] rhwau]
Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwly mUrK mnu`K cqurweIAW krdy hn (qy AwKdy hn ik AsIN qIrQ-ieSnwn Awidk puMn-krm krdy hW[)
(pr Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwlw mnu`K) bwhroN ikqnw BI pivqR krm krn vwlw hovy (prmwqmw dI hzUrI ivc) prvwn nhIN huMdw[
(auh jgq ivc Awqmk jIvn vloN) ijho ijhw (^wlI AwauNdw hY auho ijhw (^wlI) hI clw jWdw hY (jgq ivc) AOgux kr kr ky (Aw^r) pCqWdw hI (jWdw) hY ]2]
Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwly mnu`K nUM, mwieAw dy moh ivc AMnHy hoey mnu`K nUM (shI jIvn-jugiq bwry) kuJ nhIN AhuVdw[
(ipCly jnmW ivc mnmuKqw dy ADIn kIqy krmW Anuswr) Awqmk mOq (dy sMskwr Awpxy mn dI p`tI au~qy) ilKw ky auh (jgq ivc) AwauNdw hY (ieQy BI aus nUM) smJ nhIN pYNdI[
Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qur ky hI krm krdw rihMdw hY, (shI jIvn-jugiq dI sUJ) hwsl nhIN krdw, qy prmwqmw dy nwm qoN vWijAW rih ky mnu`Kw jnm AjweIN gvw jWdw hY ]3]
sdw-iQr pRBU dw nwm ismrn hI krn-jog kMm hY, gurU dw Sbd (ihrdy ivc vswxw hI) sRySt (au~dm) hY[
pUry gurU dI rwhIN hI ivkwrW qoN ^lwsI pwx dw drvwzw l`Bdw hY[
(gurU ijn@W nUM) hr vyly AwpxI bwxI dI rwhIN Awpxy Sbd dI rwhIN (prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh) suxWdw rihMdw hY, auh sdw-iQr pRBU dy nwm ivc rMgy jWdy hn, auh aus dy pRym-rMg ivc rMgy jWdy hn ]4]
ijs mnu`K dI jIB pUrI lgn lw ky prmwqmw dy nwm-rs ivc rMgI jWdI hY,
aus dw mn Awqmk Afolqw ivc msq rihMdw hY, aus dw srIr pRym-rMg ivc mgn rihMdw hY[
Awqmk Afolqw ivc itk ky auh ipAwry pRIqm pRBU nUM iml pYNdw hY, auh sdw Awqmk Afolqw ivc hI lIn rihMdw hY ]5]
ijs mnu`K dy ihrdy ivc lgn hY, auhI sdw prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh dy gIq gWdw hY[
auh gurU dy Sbd ivc juJ ky Awqmk Afolqw ivc Awqmk AwnMd ivc mgn hoieAw rihMdw hY[
mYN sdw auhnW bMidAW qoN sdky jWdw hW, ijn@W ny gurU dI d`sI kwr ivc Awpxw ic`q lwieAw hoieAw hY ]6]
ijn@W dw mn sdw-iQr pRBU dw nwm ismr ky sdw-iQr dI Xwd ivc ig`iJAw rihMdw hY,
gurU dI ikrpw nwl ijn@W mnu`KW dw ihrdw (is&q-swlwh dy rs nwl) iB`ijAw rihMdw hY,
auh sRySt AMqr Awqmy ivc itk ky prmwqmw dy gux gWdy rihMdy hn[ pRBU Awp hI auhnW nUM ieh srDw b^Sdw hY ik is&q-swlwh dI kwr hI shI jIvn-kwr hY ]7]
pr pRBU dw nwm ismrn dI sUJ auhI mnu`K hwsl krdw hY, ijs au~qy pRBU imhr dI ingwh krdw hY[
