jy (mnu`K) gurU nUM (AwpxI izMdgI dw) Awsrw-prnw bxw ley, qW aus nUM ieh BwrI ie`zq imldI hY,
ik auh prmwqmw aus dy mn ivc Aw v`sdw hY ijs nUM dunIAw vwlI koeI icMqw poh nhIN skdI[
prmwqmw (mwno) iek Pldwr ru`K hY ijs ivcoN Awqmk jIvn dyx vwlw nwm-rs coNdw hY[ ijs mnu`K ny (auh rs) pI ilAw, nwm-rs ny aus dI (mwieAw dI) qRyh dUr kr id`qI ]1]
mYN sdky hW kurbwn hW (prmwqmw qoN), auh sdw-iQr rihx vwlw prmwqmw swD-sMgq ivc imlw ky (Awpxy crnW ivc) joV lYNdw hY[
prmwqmw Awp hI swD sMgq dw myl krdw hY[ (jyhVw mnu`K swD sMgq ivc juVdw hY auh) gurU dy Sbd dI rwhIN prmwqmw dy gux gWdw hY ]1] rhwau]
